headline: Indian MedTech Company Makes a Global Mark at PCR London Valves 2025
summary: Underscoring India's rising influence in global cardiovascular innovation, Meril Life Sciences presented the one-year outcomes from the pivotal LANDMARK Randomized Controlled Trial (RCT) during the Late-Breaking Trial sessions at PCR London Valves 2025, one of the world's most respected structural heart conferences.
